  "description": "<p>如果说720P是高清，1080P是“超清”，那再往上怎么说？我看到公交车广告说4K是“极清”，那我们索性管日本已经在戛纳展映过的8K分辨率叫“变态清”好了。<strong>为了配合东京申办2020年奥运会，日本政府决定2014年开始4K数码广播，2020年开始8K数码广播。</strong>尽管4K电视机已经开售，但片源稀少，好在随着NHK开始用4K摄像机转播常规相扑比赛，相信以后会逐渐改观。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2db15789/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242239.htm&amp;t=%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%B0%86%E5%9C%A82020%E5%B9%B4%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA8K%E2%80%9C%E5%8F%98%E6%80%81%E6%B8%85%E2%80%9D%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%86%E8%8A%82%E7%9B%AE\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242239.htm&amp;t=%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%B0%86%E5%9C%A82020%E5%B9%B4%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA8K%E2%80%9C%E5%8F%98%E6%80%81%E6%B8%85%E2%80%9D%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%86%E8%8A%82%E7%9B%AE\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242239.htm&amp;t=%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%B0%86%E5%9C%A82020%E5%B9%B4%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA8K%E2%80%9C%E5%8F%98%E6%80%81%E6%B8%85%E2%80%9D%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%86%E8%8A%82%E7%9B%AE\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242239.htm&amp;t=%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%B0%86%E5%9C%A82020%E5%B9%B4%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA8K%E2%80%9C%E5%8F%98%E6%80%81%E6%B8%85%E2%80%9D%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%86%E8%8A%82%E7%9B%AE\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242239.ht